properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const s3 = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('ikfkfreeksides').value[0];const c2 = thisProperty.propertyGroup(4)('C2 Group')('Contents')('C2').size[0] * 0.5;const c1 = thisProperty.propertyGroup(4)('C1 Group')('Contents')('C1').size[0] * 0.5;let A, r3a, r3b;try {    A = Math.acos(clamp((c1 - c2) / s3, -1, 1));    r3a = [-(c2 * Math.sin(A)), -(s3 + c2 * Math.cos(A))];    r3b = [-(c1 * Math.sin(A)), -(c1 * Math.cos(A))];} catch (err) {    value;}createPath(points = [[0 - r3a[0], r3a[1]], r3a, r3b, [0 - r3b[0], r3b[1]]], [], [], true);

properties.name: Path
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const s1 = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('ikfkfreeksides').value[1];const a1 = degreesToRadians(endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('ikfkfreekangles').value[1]);const c2 = thisProperty.propertyGroup(4)('C2 Group')('Contents')('C2').size[0] * 0.5;const c3 = thisProperty.propertyGroup(4)('C3 Group')('Contents')('C3').size[0] * 0.5;const ptr = thisLayer.effect('Realistic Forearm')('Proximal Tangent Right') * 0.01;const dtr = thisLayer.effect('Realistic Forearm')('Distal Tangent Right') * 0.01;const ptl = thisLayer.effect('Realistic Forearm')('Proximal Tangent Left') * 0.01;const dtl = thisLayer.effect('Realistic Forearm')('Distal Tangent Left') * 0.01;let A, r3a, r3b;try {    A = Math.acos(clamp((c2 - c3) / s1, -1, 1));    p1 = [-(c3 * Math.sin(A)), -(s1 + c3 * Math.cos(A))];    p2 = [-(c2 * Math.sin(A)), -(c2 * Math.cos(A))];} catch (err) {    value;}const p0 = [0 - p1[0], p1[1]];const p3 = [0 - p2[0], p2[1]];createPath([p0, p1, p2, p3], [[0, s1 * dtl], [0,0], [0, -(s1 * ptr)], [0,0]], [[0,0], [0, s1 * dtr], [0,0], [0, -(s1 * ptl)]], true);
